org.jactr.core.chunktype.basic

Class BasicSymbolicChunkType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jactr.core.slot.UniqueSlotContainer
      • org.jactr.core.slot.NotifyingSlotContainer
        • org.jactr.core.chunktype.basic.BasicSymbolicChunkType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRemovableSymbolicChunkType, ISymbolicChunkType, INotifyingSlotContainer, ISlotContainer, IUniqueSlotContainer, IAdaptable

    public class BasicSymbolicChunkType
extends NotifyingSlotContainer
implements IRemovableSymbolicChunkType
    default impl. All slots and parenting must be resolved before the given chunktype is encoded. parents must be encoded as well. chunks, however, can be added after encoding
    Author:
    harrison
